Simple PHP Framework
********************

@author Anton Zekeriev Rodin inspired on tutorial from website www.anantgarg.com
@link www.azrodin.com
@licence MIT you are free to use it for all purposes.

1. Model based on ezSQL developed by www.justinvincent.com. You can connect with MySQL, Oracle, PostreSQL etc
2. All functions are well commented.
3. MVC pattern and strong OOP. Autoload class sistem.
4. Easy to install.
5. Tested on PHP 5.3.2-1ubunutu4.9 (PHP 5+ are required)
6. SEO frendly URLS.
7. Support jQuery and AJAX, like in wordpress.
8. Support for multilanguage.